{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban online profiles without a person\u2019s name/image unless verified",
        "additional_details": "Faceless profiles (i.e profiles without a person\u2019s name and image) should not be able to post, like or share without verifying who they are. With the government's help, we can restrict the creation of these faceless profiles, safeguarding our children and online communities by banning those who break the rules.",
        "background": "Cyber bullying has been an ever-increasing problem since social media's inception and enough isn't done to tackle it. It is too easy for people to make a faceless profile and post without repercussions, which can harm and destroy lives.",
